    "These strategies enabled us to depict the molecule in a more meticulous manner and was testified to improve the GNN's prediction in terms of RMSE and PCC.",
    "Furthermore, we also attempted to explore relational GNN in the drug response prediction task, which describes edges as different relations and develops distinct message passing patterns for them.",
    "It was shown that RGCN outperformed GCN without edge features.",
    "However, due to the limited GPU resources, we were not able to train the RGAT model with an optimal batch size.",
    "This part of experiments is left for future investigations."
